list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: HUGE DEBUG IN GROUP COMMUNICATION -Added support for usage of different ports, both ad applicative and middleware level --Made GroupManager be created with Socket instead String (hostname) --Made MessagingMiddleware be created with Socket instead String (hostname) -Divided Main.main into sub-functions for maintainability -Made PrimitiveParser work with ObjectStreams instead of custom interfaces --Deleted NetworkReader.java and NetworkWriter.java --Deleted PrimitiveParserRunnable.writeObjectSafe, readObjectSafe -NodeInfo tracks streams also, not only socket --2 setters for socket, the one with a boolean arg can initialize the streams --Update LeaderGroupManager, OrdinaryGroupManager so to use the correct setters (if the streams has already been created, they shouldn't be created again)

task.summary: Default task
Add BrokenProtocolException
Update PrimitiveParser, ServerSocketRunnable Finalized generic instantiation in ServerSocketRunnable Removed method PrimitiveParser.getInstance
Update GroupManager -Generified GroupManager -Made GroupManager.join return the initial data (received after synch) -Finalized JOIN and JOINING behaviour
Update JoinGroupUseCase -Removed JOIN and JOINING (must be into GroupManager for side-effects) -Removed methods -Made JoinGroupUseCase.synch return the received map -Simplified forEach calls
Update MessagingMiddleware, MessagingMiddlewareImpl -Made MessagingMiddleware.join return the received map -Added support for generic typed Group Manager
Update BrokenProtocolException Extending IllegalStateException instead of IllegalArgumentException
Add Primitive (marker interface) and PrimitiveOps (containing utility validation methods)
Update DataOperations, GroupCommands -Implementing Primitive marker interface -Added 'LEAVE' to GroupCommands
Update GroupManager, Deleted JoinGroupUseCase.java -Moved JoinGroupUseCase operations into GroupManager.join -Finalized and documented GroupManager
Update GroupManager -Managed IOException in the constructor, converted to a BrokenProtocolException
Update MessagingMiddleware, MessagingMiddlewareImpl -Added generic type ApplicationPrimitive to both to allow to specify it at application level -Generified MessagingMiddlewareImpl
Update Main -Adapted to latest commits
Moved DataOperations to application level
Update ClientCommandListener, Main -Adapted to generification of MessagingMiddlewareImpl
Fixed some warnings
Fixed more warnings
Update NodeInfo, P2PConnection, VectorClocksManager -Replaced boilerplate code using Lombok -removed useless method in P2PConnection
Update DatabaseManager, Removed Database.java - DatabaseManager made a singleton class - Added primitives to DatabaseManager - Replaced Database.java with a simple HashMap
Update DatabaseManager - Replaced implementation of the database with an hashtable to grant thread-safe behaviour
Update DatabaseManager Removed useless modules
Update ClientCommandListener Extended ClientCommandListener.parseCommand method
Update Main Added DatabaseManager initialization and usage
Javadoc Main
Update Main - Changed parsing exception behaviour

Add NetworkReader, NetworkWriter Custom functional interfaces to read and write objects. Intended to be used with lambdas in order to allow specification of classes exploiting network communication transparently
Add ParsingFunction Functional interface allowing developers to use 'writerFunction' and 'readerFunction' transparently when specifying the code used to parse 'primitive'
Update PrimitiveParser, ServerSocketRunnable Exploiting new functional interfaces to allow a safer and cleaner implementation
Update ParsingFunction, PrimitiveParser ParsingFunction.parse throwing ParsingException
Update GroupManager Made actually an interface
Update GroupManagerImpl, Delete P2PConnection.java Exploiting ParsingFunction to achieve the functionality of P2PConnection.java
Update Primitive, Delete PrimitiveOps.java Moved utility method Primitive.checkEquals from PrimitiveOps.java
Moved Message, MessageConsumer, MessageProducer, MessageProducerImpl to 'messages' package
Update DatabaseManager Cleaned instantiation
Code cleanup
Moved stuff, adapted Main to DatabaseManager changes
Increased transparency, improved packaging
Automatic code cleanup, removed eclipse files
Update NodeInfo -removed unneeded attributes -added NodeInfo.getSocket
Made PrimitiveParser final

Update GroupManagerImpl -Managed all commands except GroupCommands.SYNC -Reduced ACK usage (channels are reliable, so they're only needed for synchronization among processes [like resume execution after JOINING])
Update GroupManagerImpl -Made JOINING behaviour more robust
Update GroupManagerImpl, MessagingMiddleware, MessagingMiddlewareImpl Activated a local lock in MessagingMiddleware that enables to stop all (active) operations while a new replica is joining
Added VectorClocksTest
Update VectorClocks, VectorClocksTest -simplified VectorClocks.update -Fixed VectorClocksTest with new constructor -Added a couple test cases
Update VectorClocks -Added clone method
Made GroupManager an abstract class
